-- AngloGold Shut Its Siguiri Mine For Two Days, Business Day Says
-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 2011-01-28T05:00:53Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-01-28/anglogold-shut-its-siguiri-mine-in-guinea-for-two-days-business-day-says.html
  AngloGold Ashanti Ltd . closed its
Siguiri mine in  Guinea  for two days this week because of
demonstrations by local youths, Business Day reported.  Operations resumed yesterday after the provincial governor
stepped in, the Johannesburg-based newspaper said, citing
company spokesman  Alan Fine .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
